            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "北角巴士撞爆石壆．有片｜熱心市民合力搬大石 途人：咁重點移到呀？",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3eaaafffb2218d01e852ff8a02c2acaf/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250418/_2025041801463361411.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>北角英皇道昨日（17日）傍晚發生罕見車禍，一輛A11號機場巴士沿英皇道行駛，至新光戲院對出時突然失控，撞毀路中分隔欄，碎石四散，交通受阻。從事後網上短片可見，期間有多名熱心市民走出路中，嘗試合力移走擋在馬路中間的大石，惟大石重量非輕，引來途人議論紛紛。\n\n</p>\n<p>該段影片一開始，只見肇事城巴車頭晾在分隔欄上，橫亙3條行車線，大量磚塊亦跌出馬路，途人爭相舉起手機拍攝，並議論紛紛說：「嘩！好勁喎！」、「嘩、撞到咁喎！」、「無事嘞，無事嘞」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4201757/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一名背着背囊、穿四腳骨褲男子從行人路走向馬路中間，一聲不響彎下身，嘗試獨力移走一塊擋在路中的大塊踤石。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b205b8f6dab8852ce7ce3e648589b688/2025-04/Screenshot_2025-04-17_at_6_11_54_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一名背着背囊、穿四腳骨褲男子從行人路走向馬路中間，一聲不響彎下身，嘗試獨力移走一塊擋在路中的大塊踤石。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4201758/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"很快有另一名穿黑衣男子加入。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9216cc54e007b1309a2b0599f56e3064/2025-04/Screenshot_2025-04-17_at_6_11_57_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        很快有另一名穿黑衣男子加入。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4201759/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"二人出盡氣力。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/893401b516a36a10ba7ba302548582a8/2025-04/Screenshot_2025-04-17_at_6_11_59_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        二人出盡氣力。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4201760/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"更彎下身借力。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/76718f799b4c0be753cf2bd5714c0248/2025-04/Screenshot_2025-04-17_at_6_12_02_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        更彎下身借力。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4201761/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"但最終因大石太重，無功而還。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b6376ab321b1758213faf71a6bb40a05/2025-04/Screenshot_2025-04-17_at_6_12_27_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        但最終因大石太重，無功而還。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4201762/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"其後兩男和另一名戴帽漢則再次「挑戰」搬起大石。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/880413c8e0584b9760731d5eb404b132/2025-04/Screenshot_2025-04-17_at_6_12_34_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        其後兩男和另一名戴帽漢則再次「挑戰」搬起大石。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4201763/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"在影片結束前，三人疑似成功合力抬起大石，但未知最終能否順利移離馬路。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fb31939b9c2a5f3327c0953041e46a09/2025-04/Screenshot_2025-04-17_at_6_12_43_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        在影片結束前，三人疑似成功合力抬起大石，但未知最終能否順利移離馬路。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>未幾，一名背着背囊、穿四腳骨褲男子從行人路走向馬路中間，一聲不響彎下身，嘗試獨力移走一塊擋在路中的大塊踤石，很快有另一名穿黑衣男子加入，二人出盡氣力，更彎下身借力，但最終因大石太重，無功而還。\n\n</p>\n<p>當二人準備放棄之際，再有至少5名男子走出視察，有人更戴上手套，而剛才的兩名男子和另一名戴帽漢則再次「挑戰」搬起大石，拍片者不禁質疑：「咁重點移到呀？」在影片結束前，三人疑似成功合力抬起大石，但未知最終能否順利移離馬路。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p>昨日傍晚6時許，一輛A11號機場巴士沿英皇道行駛，至新光戲院對出時突然失控，撞毀路中分隔欄，事件中，57歲姓陸男司機報稱頸痛及手擦傷，清醒送往東區醫院治理，警方正調查意外原因。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2064554/即時-港聞-北角巴士撞爆石壆-有片-熱心市民合力搬大石-途人-咁重點移到呀",
